{"tid":1731180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國留學生支持你們","createTime":"2019-11-17T16:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T03:35:06.000Z","uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"867f0a23309b7feb9339f73a6df16a226187fa17","tid":1731180,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:17:40.000Z","msg":"巿民感謝警務人員盡忠職守，以下為部分感謝信。<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群英國留學生，看到近日在香港發生的事我們很心痛。我們特意寄這封信，是希望多謝你們，以及讓你們知道還有很多人支持你們。你們一定要加油，不要放棄！雖然這封信可能微不足道，但我們亦希望為你們打氣，暴風雨總會過去！<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1147/images/20191106_1c6f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1147%2Fimages%2F20191106_1c6f3.jpg&h=e33cb976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝香港警察連月來以無比專業的態度，以血肉之軀守護香港。你們展現無比的勇氣，面對辱罵、誣衊與攻擊，請千萬不要氣餒，香港大部分市民的眼睛是雪亮的，我們由始至終都堅定支持香港警察，你們的努力絕不會白費。"},{"pid":"b065ab274c55a401d2026a2a2eeb416d504e3db9","tid":1731180,"uid":256914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"收皮喇"},{"pid":"8ec1a080581f71df477a7fe9d53d04fd966e4e7b","tid":1731180,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:20:56.000Z","msg":"狗隻死全家<br />\n第一個生畸胎<br />\n畸形狗仔冇屎忽"},{"pid":"11e995f80b64c38e12a79e0d655b4c8f68eb87a2","tid":1731180,"uid":169074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:21:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"111c3aef6a648f992f0cdbe97b72fed8e8a140b7","tid":1731180,"uid":195048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:24:28.000Z","msg":"作好啲啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"b8376de6d7887a67adc61b2e169483bf896598f7","tid":1731180,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"111c3aef6a648f992f0cdbe97b72fed8e8a140b7","tid":1731180,"uid":195048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:24:28.000Z","msg":"作好啲啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:51:10.000Z","msg":"由警方網站提供"},{"pid":"ed82df5ffc69cb3a9e6791ca7c5c498afe2a3ed6